## Thread Dump Analysis

### Install Liberty Server

[Install Liberty](https://github.ibm.com/maximo-application-suite/knowledge-center/blob/main/devops/liberty/01-Liberty-Setup.md)

### Deploy the Application

Download the sample application [here](https://github.ibm.com/maximo-application-suite/knowledge-center/raw/refs/heads/main/java/thread-dump/sleeper.war)

Copy the war file into /home/admin/apps/webprofile-8/usr/servers/appserver/dropins

Restart the server.

The code:

```Java
package cdy.sample;

